records.addlTxt: 11:52 AM Defendant, Sirae Annie Kettula, appeared.  Atty. Daniel Patrick Steffen appeared on behalf of State of Wisconsin.  Def by phone.  Court reviews, def under DJOC with the State, restitution is part of DJOC, def behind on restitution payments- still owes over $5000 and wants to extend the DJOC to allow more time to pay restitution.  Court asks for financial/employment information from def, def provides.  State wants to extend the agreement for 2 years.  Court asks if def agrees to extend for 2 years; def does.  State to amend DJOC to include making $250 monthly payments on restitution.  Court grants the extension- agreement will be amended and modified to include the extension and include the monthly payment amount.  DA Steffen to mail amended agreement to def, def to sign and return as quickly as possible, and the agreement will be entered as an order.
